<emphasis box="[729,784,1472,1495]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="81">niger</emphasis>
(black) and 
<emphasis box="[924,976,1472,1495]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="81">apex</emphasis>
(tip), referring to its black apices of elytra.
</paragraph>
